This is a multiplayer card game called "TheMessage" using Unity(C#) and PhotonNetwork.

Each Player begins with 3 cards, and draws 2 cards when his/her turn starts. To win the game, he/her shall collect 3 cards(message) of the same color.

At the beginning of the turn, player who start will choose a card to pass the message(hidden), other players can choose to accept or pass the card to other players.
During the passing state, players can choose to intercept, lock someone(locked player must accept the coming message), block someone(blocked player cannot accept the coming message)

Player who receives 3 black cards dies. Player who receive 3 red/blue cards wins.
